{"tid":1537326,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"論\"制服\"一詞在新聞的使用","createTime":"2019-09-04T01:37:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T01:40:40.000Z","uid":298117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"387e1b3eeef17f0033cc8627dce568d69064c8e9","tid":1537326,"uid":298117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T01:37:41.000Z","msg":"個人感覺純分享：&quot;制服&quot;的感覺係通常用黎講壓制一D唔好的野, 例如&quot;制服&quot;打劫銀行的歹徒。但現在新聞如有線，好多都用依個詞語去形容popo &quot;制服&quot;市民，甘樣令人潛意識覺得市民做左一Ｄ不好的野被人捉到才會被人&quot;制服&quot;，以為人地係正當執法，示威者就被賦予負面標籤。<br />\n<br />\n但事實上，莫講話市民無犯過法就被捕，甚至連被捕好多都無反抗，甘係咪可以用下其他可以更準確描述同帶黎正確觀感的形容詞呢。例：&quot;手無寸鐵的市民被使用過多武力的popo壓在地上&quot;，&quot;示威者被無理壓在地上&quot;等等"},{"pid":"26cb45b97eaf34a6fa4f38a198cf1ae5bb729a01","tid":1537326,"uid":74442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T01:39:25.000Z","msg":"制乜嘢服，直頭係襲擊。"},{"pid":"96b4822d373f351cac9b3fef3bd388e854e978a7","tid":1537326,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T01:40:27.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n烏克蘭, 法國等其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮, 唔割但要小心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外可參考唔揸春袋揸輸精管方法: <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n [行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n <br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.l